The Shape of Things To Come

We are excited to introduce the Versa Ruler™, the first-ever shape-making ruler! The Versa Ruler enables you to form and lock unlimited, multi-sided shapes– with accurate measurements for every side and angle. Think of a 2D erector set of rulers that you can slide and angle around, laying perfectly flat on any even surface. The user can connect sides to form angles, which scale and skew smoothly–while also providing you the ability to independently lock angles and sides.
